{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be professional and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Quantum Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2c3e50;\n            --secondary-color: #34495e;\n            --text-color: #ecf0f1;\n            --accent-color: #1abc9c;\n            --background-color: #1f2937;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .game-section {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            width: 300px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .game-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content .btn:hover {\n            background-color: #138d75;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Quantum Studios</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#games\">Games</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"about\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p>Quantum Studios is an innovative video game development company dedicated to creating immersive and memorable gaming experiences. Founded in 2020, we are a passionate team of artists, designers, and engineers united by a love for interactive entertainment. We strive to push the boundaries of technology and storytelling to deliver games that captivate and inspire.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"games\">\n        <h2>Our Games</h2>\n        <div class=\"game-section\">\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2c3e50/ecf0f1?text=Cybernetic+Dawn\" alt=\"Cybernetic Dawn\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Cybernetic Dawn</h3>\n                    <p>A fast-paced cyberpunk RPG where choices matter. Explore a neon-drenched metropolis and uncover dark secrets.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/34495e/ecf0f1?text=Galactic+Odyssey\" alt=\"Galactic Odyssey\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Galactic Odyssey</h3>\n                    <p>Embark on an epic space adventure. Discover new worlds, forge alliances, and battle alien threats.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"game-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2c3e50/ecf0f1?text=Mystic+Chronicles\" alt=\"Mystic Chronicles\">\n                <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                    <h3>Mystic Chronicles</h3>\n                    <p>A fantasy adventure filled with magic, ancient lore, and challenging puzzles. Your legend awaits.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Interested in our work or looking to collaborate? Get in touch with us!</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Email: info@quantumstudios.com</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\">Follow us on social media!</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n            <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Twitter</a> |\n            <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Facebook</a> |\n            <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: var(--accent-color); text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;\">Instagram</a>\n        </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Quantum Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}